eu.cqse.check.framework.core

Class CheckInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.cqse.check.framework.core.CheckInstance

  • public class CheckInstance
extends java.lang.Object
    A instance of a custom check. Multiple CheckInstances of one CheckImplementationBase can exist in order to be executed in parallel by multiple worker threads.
